Last year @sescavpaulista gave us a reason to await every month with excitement to see the new brochure and animation being displayed at Sesc. Thank you @robdellanoce and team for trusting us with this project and making it possible to work for our favourite organisation in Brazil.

Exploring the universe:
This poster wrapped the monthly brochure, and was designed to promote special courses about space. This design places the cosmos within an image which becomes 3D when it’s moved and folded by a reader – referencing the multi-dimensional nature of the cosmos

Last year @sescavpaulista gave us a reason to await every month with excitement to see the new brochure and animation being displayed at Sesc. Thank you @robdellanoce and team for trusting us with this project and making it possible to work for our favourite organisation in Brazil.

Democratic learning:
SESC is a Brazilian non-profit that sees education as a vital part of social transformation. They provide a diverse range of free educational programmes for all kinds of people. It’s the most important cultural and education institution in Sao Paulo.

We created an editorial system for printed and digital material, to be used throughout the 12-month duration of the courses – work that celebrated all shapes and sizes of learning.

Xmas has already started @pazholandesa2 with a special 5m tall xmas tree with the Paz Icon on top of it! 😱 Happy I am living long enough to see this... who would have thought?! 😁

Paz Holandesa is a free hospital in Arequipa, Peru. It was founded in honour of child cancer patient Tony Molleapaza, whose memory is cherished by the city. 
Since 2005, Paz and friends have gone from logos to stationery, signage, wall paintings, games, editorial design to friendly characters.

Five years since starting my design studio, working side by side with my dear friend and creative partner @chrysostomosnaselos. It hasn't been easy, but it's worth every second of it.
.
I could not have done it without Chrys and the friends that surrounded us in this space. But most importantly, thanks to everyone who gave us a huge push when we started and continue to trust us with their work.
.
This post is dedicated to all the ones that choose to live an independent creative life.
.
#studiorejanedalbello #studiospace #celebration #chrysostomosnaselos
.
📷 @mel_castro_duarte
